Quick guide how to compile tool for covert DNS channel.

1. Prerequisites
You are going to need following build tools:

Cmake <=3.5.1
GNU make <= 3.81

You are going to need dev. versions of following libraries:

ncurses (>=5.9)
c-ares (>=1.10.0)
openssl (>=1.0.0)
zlib (>=0.9)

2. Installation
We recommend you to use "out of source" build when using CMake to
keep source code hierarchy clean.

Enter build folder in project root directory and run following commands

cmake ..
make

Now your build directory contains "dns-cc" executable file that is ready to 
be used. 
